OL,3,CA village pub reopens after 12 years
OL,4,Cafter being saved by its locals
OL,6,FA 300 year old Cheshire village pub
OL,7,Fhas been officially reopened after its
OL,8,Flocals clubbed together to save and
OL,9,Frestore it.
OL,11,FThe Golden Lion in Ashton Hayes, near
OL,12,FDelamere Forest, shut abruptly 12
OL,13,Fyears ago and fell into disrepair.
OL,15,FBut now the pub has been brought back
OL,16,Fto life thanks to the investment of
OL,17,Fthe local community.
