OL,3,CA village pub reopens after 12 years
OL,4,Cafter being saved by its locals
OL,6,FLance Warburton, the new landlord,
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's taken a little while to
OL,8,Fget here, but we're delighted to be
OL,9,Fopen."
OL,11,F"The support of the village, from the
OL,12,Fmoment we started work, has been
OL,13,Fexcellent. We will look to be the
OL,14,Fheart of the community."
OL,16,FChair of Ashton Hayes Community Hub
OL,17,FLtd, Hugo Deynem, said: "Lance and his
OL,18,Fteam will be an excellent fit for the
OL,19,Fvision the community has for our
OL,20,Fhighly valued village pub."
