OL,6,F"As the landlord, we will be
OL,7,Fsupporting Lance wherever possible but
OL,8,Fallowing him to run his own business,
OL,9,Fdelivering an outstanding rural pub,
OL,10,Fproviding a village focal point,
OL,11,Fserving excellent food and a wide
OL,12,Fvariety of beers and drinks."
